## Type Generation

- **Database models:** Generated from {{ORM}} schema (e.g., `prisma generate`)
- **API contracts:** Shared types between frontend and backend
- **Location:** `{{SHARED_TYPES_PATH}}`
- **Regeneration:** Run `{{TYPE_GEN_CMD}}` after schema changes

